      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i need to vent about something weird. i was talking to my landlord today about the rent increase and i could literally feel it in my teeth... like there was this sharp, discordant vibration in his voice when he said the price was fixed. i can always tell when people are lying, it's like a frequency shift. do you think that's a real thing? like a physical reaction to their pitch changing?",
